OL,7,FA hair salon is in the running for a
OL,8,Fnational award for its work supporting
OL,9,Fpeople with disabilities into
OL,10,Femployment.
OL,12,FAquarius Hair Salon, in Earlston,
OL,13,Fcreates opportunities for those with
OL,14,Flearning difficulties.
OL,16,FMegan Bilsland who has down syndrome
OL,17,Fis one of the longest standing
OL,18,Femployees having worked there for 18
OL,19,Fyears.
