OL,7,FShe said: "When I first started I was
OL,8,F13-years-old and I loved working here.
OL,9,FI enjoy talking to the clients,
OL,10,Fsometimes I do a bit of shampooing,
OL,11,Fand some sweeping up.
OL,13,F"I have done an NVQ Level One in
OL,14,Fhairdressing, it was amazing, I
OL,15,Fabsolutely loved it. I love working
OL,16,Fwith Morag, she has been amazing and
OL,17,Fso supportive.
OL,19,F"She is a really good help."
