OL,4,Caward for supporting people with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FMorag Sterrick is the owner of the
OL,8,Fsalon and is passionate about
OL,9,Fpromoting inclusion and equal
OL,10,Fopportunities.
OL,12,FShe said: "People ask me why I do it,
OL,13,Fbut the answer is, why not?
OL,15,F"Everyone needs an opportunity,
OL,16,Feveryone needs a chance. The
OL,17,Fadditional needs people that we have
OL,18,Fworked with over the years are all
OL,19,Fkeen and enthusiastic and all eager to
OL,20,Flearn.
