OL,7,F"It is good for my business and it is
OL,8,Fgood for the community. It is also
OL,9,Fgood for them and we all learn from
OL,10,Feach other.
OL,12,F"People think that disabled people
OL,13,Fcan't learn and that is completely
OL,14,Fwrong. They can learn perfectly well,
OL,15,Fyou need patience, the ability to
OL,16,Fadapt and a willingness to let people
OL,17,Ffind their feet."
